<plot>RoughRider is a low budget, tongue-in-cheek action comedy about a skateboarder by the name of Jack Urban, who seeks to avenge the death of his girlfriend Sam - her life taken by the top city drug lord known only as 'King.' With the help of his close friends, Blindside and Skip, Jack learns the whereabouts of King. As inner conflicts arise on whether or not to become a killer himself, Jack ponders his decision to kill King. But there is one problem - aware of Jack's threat, now King is chasing Jack! Jack is forced to fight in the battle of his life and his vigilantism drives his him closer to become the crime-fighting, skater-crusader known as the 'RoughRider.'</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?469162</url></doc>
